teal.physics

Interface GeneratesG

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ball, GenericGField

    public interface GeneratesG
    Objects that generate a Gravitational field should implement GeneratesG. When a World responds to getG requests, it will only sum up the gravitational fields of GeneratesG objects.
